          Session Two:
          <ul>
            <li>
              July 25 through October 30 Session Competition (15 weeks) OCTOBER 30 IS A WEDNESDAY BECAUSE WE WILL NOT PLAY ON HALLOWEEN
              <ul>
                <li>Stableford Competition</li>
                <li>Flight Competition</li>
